{"he12d0f9eg8b6dg407dg9f40g395ac779c8b8": ["It's all right, children. They didn't mean it. ", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "da6d566c-7505-1d19-7483-19c53cdd210e"], "h91670cf7ge0d7g424egbe9cge5decfd9a141": ["We have training to do. Come on.", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "da6d566c-7505-1d19-7483-19c53cdd210e"], "hcd62d836g72bdg47b5g9315gdde4f0bf81e0": ["Am I supposed to hug you, or...", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "da6d566c-7505-1d19-7483-19c53cdd210e"], "heca3a96cg8da1g4eb7g8d1fg725d36eaa643": ["Keep your blades up, children. ", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "c9a20d72-28ce-fc75-a2e0-e7ddd499dcb6"], "h12319ca6geb3fg4579g882dg60595043edd2": ["Keep your feet planted. ", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "f175a549-220f-d087-5ffb-d9f33ba83060"], "hb2c94993gf409g4b85gb7f2g2d84023961fa": ["Remember: you have teeth and claws! Use them.", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "53438108-a93d-c525-6a9a-de5a19823aa7"], "h4f98a8afg006dg4452gb8e7g488614ba725b": ["Don't fight fair. Fight to live.", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "b4d0cb97-a169-5cad-6736-db3213515511"], "ha55d2e8fgcac4g49f7g90b0gec29e871b679": ["Any questions, children? ", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "0738c1b9-b310-06eb-6b3c-b3c756479022"], "h821b530dgb3e8g4580gbe83g328c6dede36a": ["No questions? All right.", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_AD_TrainerLessons.html", "1b